DOCTOR@HAND

An online private GP service delivered by Doctor Care Anywhere working with AXA PPP. With continuing challenges of NHS GP appointment waiting times and availability, coupled with busy work and home lives, Doctor@Hand provides a fast, convenient and expert route for your employees to access a GP.  Your employees can speak, by phone or webchat to a UK GMC registered GP, all of whom are specially trained in virtual consultation skills. They can provide medical guidance, advice, diagnosis and onward referrals. In addition, they can even provide a private prescription to be delivered to your employees at home or at work.
Name: DOCTOR@HAND
